examples.text: Fırsatı varken beni neden sikmediğini anlayamıyorum.
examples.translation: I can't understand why they didn't fuck me while they had the chance.

examples.text: Bahtsız bedeviyi çölde kutup ayısı siker.
examples.translation: The unlucky bedouin gets fucked by a polar bear in the desert.

glosses: to destroy, to ruin, to fuck up, to screw up

etymology:
From Ottoman Turkish سكمك (sikmek, “to fuck, to have sexual congress with, to injure seriously, ruin”), from Proto-Turkic *sik-mek (“to copulate”). Cognate with Karakhanid سِكْماكْ (sikmēk, “to copulate”) Azerbaijani sikmək (“to fuck”), Kazakh сігу (sıgu, “to fuck”), Kyrgyz сигүү (sigüü),
Tatar сигу (siğu), Turkmen sikmek (“to fuck”), and Uzbek sikmoq (“to fuck”).
